      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-stp-val-rie-mic    to   w-stp-val-rie-tot      .
           move      037                  to   w-stp-val-rie-pos      .
           perform   stp-val-rie-tot-000  thru stp-val-rie-tot-999    .
       stp-val-rie-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
