           move      w-stp-val-rie-030    to   w-stp-val-rie-tot      .
           move      061                  to   w-stp-val-rie-pos      .
           perform   stp-val-rie-tot-000  thru stp-val-rie-tot-999    .
       stp-val-rie-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Totale 60 gg.                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-stp-val-rie-060    to   w-stp-val-rie-tot      .
           move      073                  to   w-stp-val-rie-pos      .
           perform   stp-val-rie-tot-000  thru stp-val-rie-tot-999    .
       stp-val-rie-350.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
