      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-stp-val-rie-090    to   w-stp-val-rie-tot      .
           move      085                  to   w-stp-val-rie-pos      .
           perform   stp-val-rie-tot-000  thru stp-val-rie-tot-999    .
       stp-val-rie-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Totale 120 gg.                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-stp-val-rie-120    to   w-stp-val-rie-tot      .
           move      097                  to   w-stp-val-rie-pos      .
           perform   stp-val-rie-tot-000  thru stp-val-rie-tot-999    .
       stp-val-rie-450.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
