      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-stp-val-rie-cli    to   w-stp-val-rie-tot      .
           move      121                  to   w-stp-val-rie-pos      .
           perform   stp-val-rie-tot-000  thru stp-val-rie-tot-999    .
       stp-val-rie-900.
